    "body": "On ROCm fast path routes to group_gemm_ck and slow path to _grouped_mm_fallback.\r\nBy default, fast path = False route is activated since CK path is not performant yet. \r\nTo activate CK path, use ROCM_ALLOW_GROUP_GEMM_CK=1 env variable.\r\n\r\nCherry pick of https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/170159 to release/2.10 branch.\r\n\r\ncc @jeffdaily @sunway513 @jithunnair-amd @pruthvistony @ROCmSupport @jataylo @hongxiayang @naromero77amd @pragupta @jerrymannil @xinyazhang",
